QUESTION:
Create a Persistent Volume Claim with the given specification.
CheckCompleteIncomplete
Volume Name: claim-log-1
Storage Request: 50Mi
Access Modes: ReadWriteOnce



SOLUTION:
apiVersion: v1
kind: PersistentVolumeClaim
metadata:
  name: claim-log-1
spec:
  accessModes:
       - ReadWriteOnce
  resources:
      requests:
        storage: 50Mi


